data.description: Step into luxury living with this impeccable 1800+ sq ft home in Copperas Cove, TX! Featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a plethora of new upgrades, including 12 inches of insulation, a paid-off water softener, silent garage door opener, UV disinfectant & reverse osmosis system, extended driveway on both sides, metal fences, gutters, storm door, new wood front door, porcelain tile with extra boxes left over, dimmable recess lighting, soft-close cabinets and drawers, pull-out pot and pan rack holder, pull-out spice rack, double oven, electrical automatic microwave drawer, titanium granite countertops, flat-top range wired for a five-top range, wine fridge, and under-cabinet lighting with color-changing capabilities and an electric fireplace in the livingroom that is mounted and will stay with the home. Luxuriate in the rain-down walk-in shower and enjoy the heating and lighting with defrost mirror and double floating vanity. This home is ideally situated near a great school and thriving community. Don't miss your chance to see it today
